'''格拉斯哥'''（{{lang en|Glasgow}}），是[[美国|美国]]西北部[[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]的一座城镇，亦是[[瓦利縣_(蒙大拿州)|瓦利縣]]縣治所在。{{GR|6}}根据[[2010年美国人口普查|2010年美国人口普查]]，该城镇的人口为3,250人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |title=2010 census factfinder2 |access-date=2013-08-02 |archive-date=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911234518/http://factfinder2.census.gov/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在蒙大拿州排行第24。使用[[北美山区时区|北美山区时区]]（UTC-7，夏季为UTC-6）作为标准时间。<ref name=census>{{cite web | url=http://www.census.gov/prod/www/abs/decennial/ | title=Census of Population and Housing | publisher=U.S. Census  Bureau | accessdate=November 18, 2011 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060208103743/http://www.census.gov/prod/www/abs/decennial/ | archive-date=2006-02-08 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

本城取名自蘇格蘭港口[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.montanahistory.net/placenames/indexc.htm |title=Montana History Net: Place Names (E-G) |publisher=Montanahistory.net |accessdate=April 25, 2012 |archive-date=2020-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223200412/http://www.montanahistory.net/placenames/indexc.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==地理==
格拉斯哥的座標為{{Coord|48|11|54|N|106|38|7|W|type:city}}（48.198252,-106.635402）。{{GR|1}}根據[[美國2000年人口普查|2000年人口普查]]，本城面積為{{convert|1.43|sqmi|sqkm|2}}，沒有水域。<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2012-12-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>本城海拔為{{convert|2093|ft|m}}。<ref name=epo>{{cite web |url=http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=27733 |title=Profile for Glasgow, Montana, MT |location=US-MT |publisher=ePodunk |accessdate=April 25, 2012 |archive-date=2019-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515083021/http://epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=27733 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

